headline: Is Iron Mountain Incorporated (IRM) Trading at a Compelling Valuation Level?
summary: Baron Funds, an investment management company, released its “Baron Real Estate Income Fund” second-quarter 2025 investor letter. A copy of the letter can be downloaded here.
